### 2.3 Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,DB: Card Drag-and-Drop Flow

    U->>FE: Drag card to new column
    FE->>FE: Calculate new position (fractional)
    FE->>FE: Optimistic UI update
    FE->>API: PATCH /api/cards/:id/move
    API->>API: Validate request
    API->>DB: UPDATE cards SET column_id, position
    DB-->>API: Updated card
    API-->>FE: 200 OK with card data
    alt Success
        FE->>FE: Confirm optimistic update
    else Failure
        FE->>FE: Rollback to previous state
        FE->>U: Show error toast
    end

    Note over U,DB: Reports Data Flow

    U->>FE: Navigate to Reports
    FE->>API: GET /api/reports/tasks
    API->>DB: SELECT with JOINs
    DB-->>API: Task data with board/column names
    API-->>FE: JSON array of tasks
    FE->>FE: Render AG Grid
    U->>FE: Click Export CSV
    FE->>FE: AG Grid exportDataAsCsv()
```

### 2.4 Database Schema

```mermaid
