    }

    cards {
        int id PK
        int column_id FK
        varchar(255) title
        text description
        float position
        timestamp created_at
        timestamp updated_at
    }

    boards ||--o{ columns : "has"
    columns ||--o{ cards : "contains"
```

### 2.5 State Management

#### Frontend State Architecture

| State Type | Location | Scope |
|------------|----------|-------|
| Server State | `useBoard`, `useReports` hooks | Component trees |
| UI State | Component local state | Individual components |
| Drag State | `useDragDrop` hook | Board component tree |
| Form State | Component local state | Form components |

#### Optimistic Update Pattern

```
1. User initiates action (drag card)
2. Store current state for rollback
3. Apply optimistic update to UI
4. Send API request
5. On success: discard rollback state
6. On failure: restore rollback state, show error
```

