| API Response Time | < 200ms for CRUD operations | Integration test timing |
| Drag-and-Drop Latency | < 100ms UI feedback | Manual testing |
| Reports Grid Load | < 2s for 1000 rows | Performance test with seed data |
| Initial Page Load | < 3s on local network | Lighthouse audit |
