### Appendix B: API Contract Summary

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Request Body | Response |
|--------|----------|-------------|--------------|----------|
| GET | /api/boards | List all boards | - | `[{id, name, created_at}]` |
| POST | /api/boards | Create board | `{name}` | `{id, name, created_at}` |
| GET | /api/boards/:id | Get board with columns and cards | - | `{id, name, columns: [...]}` |
| PUT | /api/boards/:id | Update board | `{name}` | `{id, name, updated_at}` |
| DELETE | /api/boards/:id | Delete board | - | `204 No Content` |
| POST | /api/boards/:boardId/columns | Create column | `{name}` | `{id, name, position}` |
| PUT | /api/columns/:id | Update column | `{name?, position?}` | `{id, name, position}` |
| DELETE | /api/columns/:id | Delete column | - | `204 No Content` |
| POST | /api/columns/:columnId/cards | Create card | `{title, description?}` | `{id, title, position}` |
| PUT | /api/cards/:id | Update card | `{title?, description?}` | `{id, title, updated_at}` |
| DELETE | /api/cards/:id | Delete card | - | `204 No Content` |
| PATCH | /api/cards/:id/move | Move card | `{columnId, position}` | `{id, column_id, position}` |
| GET | /api/reports/tasks | Get all tasks | `?boardId&status` | `[{id, title, board_name, ...}]` |
| GET | /api/reports/metrics | Get metrics | `?boardId` | `{total_cards, by_status, by_board}` |
| GET | /api/reports/export | Export CSV | `?boardId&status` | CSV file |

